ds = CartoDataSource(user='', api_key='')
ds._sql_client = mock.MagicMock()
ds._sql_client.send.return_value = {'rows': [], 'time': 42.0, 'fields': {},
    'total_rows': 0}
result = ds.query('some query')
ds._sql_client.send.assert_called_with('some query', do_post=False, format=
    'json', parse_json=True)
self.assertEqual([], result.rows)
self.assertEqual(42, result.meta['response_time'])
